Description: Donut Bun, a donut bun maker, a few seconds for a new hair style. Use it this way : Pull hair back into a ponytail and secure it with a rubber band. Pull the pony through foam donut hole until it comfortably sits on the head. You can secure it with bobby pins if it feels loose. Separate hair into 4 equal sections, and spread them across the donut, until it's completely covered. Wrap and tuck the ends under the foam and pin them down. Spray with hairspray to tame flyaways and set your style.

The Pantene All Day Smooth Miracle Water from their Silky Smooth Care range will help you in keeping your hair healthy. This unisex non-sticky haircare serum from Pantene is very light. When this Silky Smooth Care Miracle Water comes in contact with your hair, it will change to a clear liquid which in turn releases the water content infused in this Pantene Miracle Water. This action will leave an ultra-light finish to your hair that will help them maintain their natural moisture. Directions to Use • Take two pumps of the Pantene Miracle Water on to your palms. • Rub your palms together to evenly spread the serum on your palms and fingers. • Gently spread this on to your hair strands. • Do not rinse away the serum.

Title: Rejsol Salicylic Acid Peel 15% Gel 50 ML with Pre Peeling Cleanser Neutralizer Moisturizer Sunscreen 750 ml(Set of 7)
Description: Salicylic Acid is a Anti Acne agent it penetrates the pores of the acne and kills the organisms. It has anti bacterial properties that kills the germs.Chemical Peels are acids therefore should be used under the Supervision of trained cosmetologists.Always do Patch Test when using the peel for the first time.Patch test: Apply small amount of peel below neck or armpit, see for any redness beyond the margin of application, if seendiscontinue the procedure. If no redness or itching continue with the procedureProcedure:Cleanse the skin with oil free cleanser, if using oil containing cleanser, after cleansing whip with alcohol or spirit. oil blocks the acid therefore desired action is not achieved.Apply Peel with brush or ear Buds, gel peels can be best applied with gloved fingers. start applying from the forehead upto the neck, application time should not be more than 20 seconds. keep peel for 3-7 mins depending on your skin habituality of peeling and the peel strength. Spray neutralizer, keep for 1 min.wash with water., apply sunscreen and good moisturiser for 7 days twice daily.Post Peel:Success of the peeling depends on sunprotection and moisturisingfirst the skin dies so becomes black don't worry this is the skin that is going to peel of itselfThere are two types of peeling microscopic that is not seen by naked eyes, and macroscopic peeling that is visualised very wellDo not remove the skin by your self.Don't use soap for 2-3 days, thereafter, use mild soap for 7-8 days, don't scrub too hardNote: If you don't get desired results doesnt mean the peel is not working it only means that your skin is tough for the peel you are using. then its time to use stronger peels or increase the application time of the peel in the next sitting.CleanserGlycolic Acid 5%Stearic Acid 0.8%Benzalkonium Chloride 0.1%Moisturising Cream:Aloevera 10%Vitamin E 0.5%Wheat Germ Oil 1.5%Urea 10%Jojoba Oil 0.1%Propylene Glycol 6%Light Liquid Paraffin 10%Glycerin 2%Titanium Dioxide 1%Benzalkonium Chloride 0.1%Methy Paraben 0.2%Sunscreen Octyl methoxy cinnamate 8.5%Avobenzone 3%Titanium Dioxide 7%Aloevera Gel 10%Wheat Germ Oil 1.5%Zinc oxide 6%Methyl Paraben 0.2%
